snippet.title: Plastiland Gameplay
snippet.description:
Download for iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/app/id949504560
Welcome to the enchanting handmade plasticine worlds! Plastiland is a charming acrade puzzle-platformer based on the Lemmings classical gameplay and inspired by Neverhood’s art style. It’s incredible fun for both adults and children!
